            The activities are designed to develop creativity, communication and self esteem. Individual and cultural diversity is 
            respected and promoted, each child is treated as an individual with different needs, culture and special cares. Serving 
            a diverse community gives us the opportunity to explore each child's heritage and traditions to enrich the learning of every
            community actor.
        </p> 

